<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-24.png" alt="" width="1854" height="1048" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-24-xs.webp 300w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-24-sm.webp 480w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-24-md.webp 768w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-24-lg.webp 1024w"></figure>
<p>打开文件夹如图所示即可。</p>
<h1>三、移动文件夹</h1>
<p><span style="color: #ba372a;">此文件夹相当于安装包安装过后在 <strong>Program Files </strong>或 <strong>Program Files(x86)</strong> 里的文件夹，如果理解可以自行选择存放位置，如不熟悉，按照步骤进行即可。</span></p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-53.png" alt="" width="1854" height="1048" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-53-xs.webp 300w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-53-sm.webp 480w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-53-md.webp 768w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-49-53-lg.webp 1024w"></figure>
<p>将文件夹全部移入C盘的 <strong>Program Files</strong> 目录下，如要索取管理员权限，点击继续即可。</p>
<p> </p>
<h1>四、安装</h1>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-50-22.png" alt="" width="1854" height="1048" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-50-22-xs.webp 300w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-50-22-sm.webp 480w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-50-22-md.webp 768w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/10/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-12-50-22-lg.webp 1024w"></figure>
<p>打开目录，并找到 <strong>QuickInstall(如果大小写有误忽略不计)</strong> ，点击<span style="color: #ba372a;">安装按钮即可</span>。</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h1><span style="color: #ba372a;">安装完成后即可在桌面看到</span></h1>
