        </author>
        <link href="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/ubuntu24041-lts-chong-ming-ming-shu-ru-kuang-wu-fa-shu-ru-zhong-wen.html"/>
        <id>https://xyz-fbw.github.io/ubuntu24041-lts-chong-ming-ming-shu-ru-kuang-wu-fa-shu-ru-zhong-wen.html</id>
        <media:content url="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47.jpg" medium="image" />
            <category term="Discoveries"/>

        <updated>2024-10-19T10:51:30+08:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                        <img src="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47.jpg" alt="" />
                    例如下方情况 方法如下 配置fctix输入法框架环境变量（个人使用vim作为文本编辑器i） sudo vim ~/.pam_environment 输入以下内容 GTK_IM_MODULE=ibus QT_IM_MODULE=ibus XMODIFIERS="@im=ibus" 保存并退出。 注销或重启后即可输入中文
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47.jpg" class="type:primaryImage" alt="" /></p>
                <h1>例如下方情况</h1>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47-2.jpg" alt="" width="881" height="544" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47-2-xs.webp 300w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47-2-sm.webp 480w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47-2-md.webp 768w ,https://xyz-fbw.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Screenshot-from-2024-10-19-18-27-47-2-lg.webp 1024w"></figure>
<h1><span style="color: #ba372a;">方法如下</span></h1>
<p data-pid="Q665PRgS">配置fctix输入法框架环境变量（个人使用vim作为文本编辑器i）</p>
<div class="highlight">
<pre><code class="language-text">sudo vim ~/.pam_environment</code></pre>
</div>
<p data-pid="cXqBa-52">输入以下内容</p>
<div class="highlight">
<pre><code class="language-text">GTK_IM_MODULE=ibus
QT_IM_MODULE=ibus
XMODIFIERS="@im=ibus"</code></pre>
</div>
<p data-pid="N0ZFm9oa">保存并退出。</p>
<h1 data-pid="N0ZFm9oa"><span style="color: #ba372a;">注销或重启后即可输入中文</span></h1>
